## Write a program to swap two numbers without using third variable

```txt
Input  : 10 20
Output : 20 10
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="swap-two-numbers-without-using-third-variable" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int var1, var2;

int main(void){

    printf("Enter two numbers: ");
    scanf("%i %i", &var1, &var2);

    printf("Before\nNumber1: %d , Number2: %d\n",var1,var2);

    var1+=var2;
    var2=var1-var2;
    var1-=var2;

    printf("\nAfter\nNumber1: %d , Number2: %d\n",var1,var2);

    return 0;
}
```

